<TEXT>
   An off-duty New York City police
officer shot and killed a man and wounded three teen-agers who
attacked him in his yard with a baseball bat Sunday when he tried
to stop a fight, authorities said.
   The fight broke out at a party next door to officer Kris
Brandt's house and spilled into his yard about 1:20 a.m., police
